00:24:16,304 --> 00:24:17,561
What are you saying?

255
00:24:17,596 --> 00:24:19,818
Everyday is too long.

256
00:24:19,853 --> 00:24:21,360
So disgusting.

257
00:24:21,395 --> 00:24:22,833
Okay, you go.

258
00:24:22,868 --> 00:24:24,383
This fella is too disgusting, I can't bring him.

259
00:24:24,609 --> 00:24:27,059
Sir, please leave well, take care.

260
00:24:27,094 --> 00:24:29,509
You, you, wait and see. You...

261
00:24:30,206 --> 00:24:31,431
Hyung Tae, thank you.

262
00:24:31,466 --> 00:24:32,841
Take care.

263
00:24:33,441 --> 00:24:34,466
Jerk.

264
00:24:43,182 --> 00:24:45,880
Marriage?

265
00:24:46,085 --> 00:24:47,786
Of course it is good.

266
00:24:48,754 --> 00:24:53,564
That gal, if I don't want her,
