Can't live on.

282
00:25:59,991 --> 00:26:01,158
Yes.

283
00:26:01,193 --> 00:26:02,647
It should be so.

284
00:26:04,510 --> 00:26:07,352
We have been together for 10 years already.

285
00:26:07,885 --> 00:26:09,432
Who else can replace her?

286
00:26:14,309 --> 00:26:15,827
Drink up.

287
00:27:01,337 --> 00:27:04,192
Oh, it's Yoon Sung Ah.

288
00:27:04,442 --> 00:27:07,598
Yoon Sung Ah, hello.

289
00:27:09,494 --> 00:27:12,294
Yes, wearing a chilli jacket.

290
00:27:12,329 --> 00:27:13,972
Why are you so cute?

291
00:27:14,007 --> 00:27:16,351
I don't know what to do with you.

292
00:27:27,557 --> 00:27:29,402
Aren't you going in?

293
00:27:30,755 --> 00:27:35,978
The weather is great.
Let's stay here for a bit before we head in.

294
00:27:46,380 --> 00:27:48,897
- When did you arrive?
- Just now.

295
00:27:50,095 --> 00:27:54,354
Recently, is it because of me,
you are shortening your practise time?

296
00:27:54,444 --> 00:27:55,284
No.

297
00:27:55,319 --> 00:27:57,205
My daily schedule, someone is in charge of it.

298
00:27:57,240 --> 00:28:00,091
I have long not being make decisions myself.

299
00:28:00,839 --> 00:28:01,789
Ah.

300
00:28:03,604 --> 00:28:04,260
Why?

301
00:28:04,295 --> 00:28:06,152
You are worried about me?

302
00:28:06,418 --> 00:28:08,727
Looks like I have nothing to worry about.

303
00:28:13,509 --> 00:28:16,282
Reeks of alcohol.

304
00:28:23,482 --> 00:28:24,750
Come in.

305
00:28:25,221 --> 00:28:26,738
When did you arrive?

306
00:28:26,773 --> 00:28:28,256
Much earlier on.

307
00:28:28,714 --> 00:28:30,432
- Very clean.
- Not bad.

308
00:28:32,422 --> 00:28:34,079
So cute.

309
00:28:35,229 --> 00:28:36,402
Living alone...

310
00:28:40,862 --> 00:28:42,895
I don't know if everyone can fit in.

311
00:28:42,990 --> 00:28:44,296
I brought fried rice vermicelli.

312
00:28:45,432 --> 00:28:47,450
We bought beer.

313
00:28:47,976 --> 00:28:49,743
Thank you.

314
00:28:50,988 --> 00:28:52,928
- Present.
- Present?

315
00:28:55,633 --> 00:28:57,210
Radio?

316
00:28:57,461 --> 00:28:59,551
You really made it?

317
00:28:59,586 --> 00:29:02,411
So pretty.

318
00:29:03,629 --> 00:29:04,843
Chun Hee.

319
00:29:04,878 --> 00:29:06,544
I will make yours.

320
00:29:06,579 --> 00:29:08,211
I am learning now.

321
00:29:08,246 --> 00:29:09,051
Really?

322
00:29:18,012 --> 00:29:20,244
- Do eat more.
- You prepared so much.

323
00:29:20,578 --> 00:29:22,168
Looks delicious.

324
00:29:24,860 --> 00:29:32,251
But, isn't there such a phrase,
a useless superior is worse than the enemy.

325
00:29:33,582 --> 00:29:36,738
Just a few days into work and
he is already talking like this.

326
00:29:36,773 --> 00:29:38,295
Let him be, Mi Kyung.

327
00:29:38,553 --> 00:29:42,297
He must show off at suitable times,
it brings meaning to earning money.

328
00:29:45,701 --> 00:29:49,129
Chun Hee, you are the one amongst us
with the most experience.

329
00:29:49,391 --> 00:29:50,649
You have worked for 10 years already, right?

330
00:29:50,684 --> 00:29:51,875
Me?

331
00:29:52,193 --> 00:29:54,546
It is a little troubling on others.

332
00:29:55,362 --> 00:29:58,689
Once I see a lazy junior, I feel terrible.

333
00:29:59,003 --> 00:30:01,796
Although they are lazy, but when it affects
their interest, they become smarter.

334
00:30:02,015 --> 00:30:03,263
I hate it when I see it.

335
00:30:03,298 --> 00:30:06,348
To Sung Ah, this must be very unfamiliar.

336
00:30:06,694 --> 00:30:08,767
I know that by saying this I will get a scolding.

337
00:30:08,802 --> 00:30:10,110
But I envy all of you.

338
00:30:10,145 --> 00:30:12,976
Superior, junior, colleagues.

339
00:30:13,239 --> 00:30:14,332
A work environment, is it not?

340
00:30:16,506 --> 00:30:19,661
I knew that I will be chided by all of you.

341
00:30:25,408 --> 00:30:27,268
You guys.

342
00:30:27,531 --> 00:30:29,118
What is love?

343
00:30:29,153 --> 00:30:32,658
This is a topic that we talk
about in school last time.

344
00:30:32,693 --> 00:30:33,988
Why are you still talking about it now?

345
00:30:34,023 --> 00:30:35,565
So mushy.

346
00:30:35,600 --> 00:30:36,574
Why?

347
00:30:36,609 --> 00:30:37,720
Tell her.

348
00:30:38,013 --> 00:30:39,139
Love.

349
00:30:40,634 --> 00:30:43,480
It can only be protected if you don't lose yourself.

350
00:30:44,569 --> 00:30:45,919
Greed.

351
00:30:46,244 --> 00:30:47,220
Living.

352
00:30:47,255 --> 00:30:49,913
Looks like once you get married,
love becomes very simple.

353
00:30:49,948 --> 00:30:53,728
It becomes more profound, you are too much.

354
00:30:54,865 --> 00:30:55,898
What about you, Sung Ah?

355
00:30:55,933 --> 00:30:56,648
Me?

356
00:30:58,851 --> 00:31:00,025
Concert.

357
00:31:00,060 --> 00:31:01,200
Why?

358
00:31:04,482 --> 00:31:08,237
Because if you don't give it your best, you will fail.

359
00:31:10,308 --> 00:31:11,823
Nan Hee?

360
00:31:17,299 --> 00:31:18,812
Timing?

361
00:31:20,344 --> 00:31:22,050
You?

362
00:31:27,209 --> 00:31:27,927
Pass.

363
00:31:28,193 --> 00:31:29,911
Quick answer.

364
00:31:29,946 --> 00:31:32,286
Rascal, say what is love.

365
00:31:32,528 --> 00:31:34,365
Hey! Hey!

366
00:31:36,771 --> 00:31:38,889
<i>Even though living is hard</i>

367
00:31:38,924 --> 00:31:41,482
<i>Even if I fall in love</i>

368
00:31:41,739 --> 00:31:46,474
<i>But someday a good day will come to me too</i>

369
00:31:46,509 --> 00:31:49,093
<i>{\a6}This is the beginning</i>

370
00:31:46,509 --> 00:31:49,093
It looks so pitiful to leave you alone behind.

371
00:31:49,128 --> 00:31:52,893
<i>{\a6}The star of life is me</i>

372
00:31:49,128 --> 00:31:52,893
Quickly, go.

373
00:31:53,101 --> 00:31:57,380
<i>{\a6}Don't forget, who you are</i>

374
00:31:53,101 --> 00:31:57,380
See you.

375
00:32:05,581 --> 00:32:06,381
We're going.

376
00:32:07,182 --> 00:32:07,582
Take care.

377
00:32:10,036 --> 00:32:11,544
<i>It's okay</i>

378
00:32:11,847 --> 00:32:13,078
<i>Don't worry </i>

379
00:32:13,795 --> 00:32:17,147
<i>It's suppose to be hard for everyone </i>

380
00:32:17,449 --> 00:32:20,656
<i>After one night's sleep </i>

381
00:32:21,187 --> 00:32:24,368
<i>Everything will be fine again </i>

382
00:32:24,672 --> 00:32:28,531
<i>I don't know how to give up</i>

383
00:32:29,094 --> 00:32:32,219
<i>I'm fine and strong </i>

384
00:32:32,457 --> 00:32:39,973
<i>Always cheerful and happy
I will patiently endure it</i>

385
00:32:40,008 --> 00:32:42,689
<i>I believe
Even though living is hard</i>

386
00:32:42,724 --> 00:32:44,558
<i>Even if I fall in love </i>

387
00:32:44,593 --> 00:32:48,392
<i>I will never cry
or complain </i>

388
00:32:48,427 --> 00:32:50,174
<i>This is the beginning</i>

389
00:32:50,209 --> 00:32:53,358
<i>The star of life is me</i>

390
00:32:53,612 --> 00:32:55,519
<i>I never don't cry</i>

391
00:32:55,851 --> 00:32:57,675
<i>Sad tears goodbye </i>

392
00:32:57,710 --> 00:32:59,499
<i>Hard worries goodbye</i>

393
00:32:59,701 --> 00:33:03,331
<i>The beautiful day that I have
imagined last night, here I come</i>

394
00:33:03,366 --> 00:33:05,459
<i>Today is the beginning </i>

395
00:33:05,826 --> 00:33:09,020
<i>I am going to do well</i>

396
00:33:09,814 --> 00:33:11,984
<i>Smile again.</i>

397
00:33:14,772 --> 00:33:15,568
Greed.

398
00:33:15,603 --> 00:33:16,571
Living.

399
00:33:16,606 --> 00:33:17,539
Concert.

400
00:33:17,777 --> 00:33:19,480
Timing.

401
00:33:19,718 --> 00:33:21,367
And, pass.

402
00:33:23,241 --> 00:33:25,273
You are suddenly concerned about love.

403
00:33:26,134 --> 00:33:29,556
Hey, why did Hyung Tae say pass?

404
00:33:29,591 --> 00:33:31,095
I roughly know why.

405
00:33:32,018 --> 00:33:32,905
What is it?

406
00:33:32,940 --> 00:33:36,253
Because someone has already said
the answer he wanted to give.

407
00:33:40,188 --> 00:33:42,745
Could it be really because of that?

408
00:33:43,804 --> 00:33:45,186
Makes people so curious.

409
00:33:46,201 --> 00:33:47,545
Chun Hee.

410
00:33:47,919 --> 00:33:49,887
Why can I see even this sort of things?

411
00:33:53,421 --> 00:33:56,075
Don't you think I will be very tired?

412
00:35:36,825 --> 00:35:38,787
What's up?

413
00:35:55,147 --> 00:35:56,609
Hold on.

414
00:35:56,644 --> 00:35:58,072
Hand!

415
00:35:58,526 --> 00:36:00,335
What happened? What happened?

416
00:36:00,976 --> 00:36:03,381
Hey, are you going to close
that door just like that?

417
00:36:03,831 --> 00:36:05,988
I was just thinking of opening the safety latch.

418
00:36:06,412 --> 00:36:07,226
It hurts?

419
00:36:07,261 --> 00:36:08,865
Of course it does!

420
00:36:19,213 --> 00:36:20,816
Do you need my help anywhere?

421
00:36:21,112 --> 00:36:24,007
Your hand is already hurting,
how else can you help?

422
00:36:24,809 --> 00:36:26,241
It will be fine, right?

423
00:36:26,276 --> 00:36:27,662
Hurts a lot?

424
00:36:28,710 --> 00:36:30,737
Do you want to go to the
hospital for a check-up?

425
00:36:30,772 --> 00:36:32,456
Just a minor injury,
why the need to go to the hospital.

426
00:36:32,491 --> 00:36:34,531
Why is your reaction so retarded?

427
00:36:34,853 --> 00:36:36,430
Once I get anxious.

428
00:36:36,915 --> 00:36:39,431
I thought you were going to close the door.

429
00:36:54,637 --> 00:36:56,238
Do it yourself.

430
00:37:05,707 --> 00:37:07,490
Why did you come?

431
00:37:08,553 --> 00:37:10,419
How are you doing?

432
00:37:12,450 --> 00:37:15,357
Didn't you ask that question just now?

433
00:37:18,806 --> 00:37:22,777
The announcement date for the selection
of the essays is just a few days away, right?

434
00:37:22,812 --> 00:37:23,527
Oh.

435
00:37:26,156 --> 00:37:27,914
Curious if you are doing well.

436
00:37:27,949 --> 00:37:29,635
Very.

437
00:37:31,676 --> 00:37:33,133
Hey.

438
00:37:33,445 --> 00:37:35,984
How come you didn't ask who's
at door before opening?

439
00:37:37,191 --> 00:37:39,854
This girl really have the guts.

440
00:37:43,291 --> 00:37:45,293
What exactly do you want?

441
00:37:48,450 --> 00:37:51,302
Could it be you forgot what you
told me at the streetside food tent?

442
00:37:51,437 --> 00:37:53,693
Didn't you say you can't be
friends with me anymore?

443
00:37:54,051 --> 00:37:56,138
But what are you doing here now?

444
00:37:57,592 --> 00:38:01,258
If we can't even be friends,
do you feel that inside it is a little empty?

445
00:38:01,293 --> 00:38:03,864
Missing me? Worrying about me?

446
00:38:05,112 --> 00:38:07,750
Every time you feel like that,
you would just barge in anytime.

447
00:38:07,785 --> 00:38:11,417
Are you going to keep treating me like a dog
who needs to be fed and just leave like this?

448
00:38:11,452 --> 00:38:13,551
When Sung Ah is upset, you are concerned.

449
00:38:13,586 --> 00:38:16,379
When my heart is hurting, you act indifferent.

450
00:38:17,087 --> 00:38:18,895
You are such a joke.

451
00:38:18,930 --> 00:38:20,618
You can only think of it as like this?

452
00:38:25,758 --> 00:38:28,162
Then what should I think it as?

453
00:38:28,197 --> 00:38:30,795
You have prepared to break off with me,
hence you said those words.

454
00:38:31,015 --> 00:38:33,440
But I don't have any preparation, and just lost
the times that we have been through together.

455
00:38:33,475 --> 00:38:37,865
I tried ways and means to protect those times,
but you ruined time in just a few moments.

456
00:38:40,777 --> 00:38:42,386
I said before,

457
00:38:42,723 --> 00:38:46,345
Losing you, is as good as losing my whole life.

458
00:38:46,380 --> 00:38:49,967
You think that there will be no sense of lose?

459
00:38:52,451 --> 00:38:55,077
If it was not unbearable, I would not have said that.

460
00:38:55,112 --> 00:38:57,504
You think that my feelings are different from yours?

461
00:38:57,539 --> 00:38:59,965
Did I take you for a little puppy every time?

462
00:39:00,199 --> 00:39:03,007
When have I ever hurt you and,
yet felt happy and free?

463
00:39:06,354 --> 00:39:08,065
Do you know why I came?

464
00:39:08,100 --> 00:39:10,756
If I didn't come to see you,
I will go crazy, so I came.

465
00:39:10,791 --> 00:39:14,182
I didn't think that much. Uncontrollably, I came.

466
00:39:14,217 --> 00:39:17,350
Not wishing to worry about you,
but still I am, hence I came.

467
00:39:17,385 --> 00:39:19,847
Without you at my side,
I am so lonely I am going crazy.

468
00:39:21,223 --> 00:39:23,723
You are living a new life in a new home.

469
00:39:24,036 --> 00:39:28,974
But me, did you ever think of me
that you left behind and how I felt?

470
00:39:31,817 --> 00:39:34,874
I lost my directions, I'm at a lost of what to do.

471
00:39:35,215 --> 00:39:36,667
That's right.

472
00:39:37,583 --> 00:39:40,054
I am lacking a lot.

473
00:39:40,256 --> 00:39:42,294
But don't you feel anything?

474
00:39:43,163 --> 00:39:46,197
How can you be so rational in everything you do?

475
00:39:48,668 --> 00:39:50,984
You only think about yourself getting hurt.

476
00:39:51,354 --> 00:39:54,383
You didn't think that you've hurt me too?

477
00:39:55,215 --> 00:39:58,240
When you left and pushed me aside,
you said want to be friends.

478
00:39:58,444 --> 00:40:00,845
You think that liking you,
I don't feel any pain at all?

479
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:04,839
You think that living under one roof,
I have an easy time controlling myself?

480
00:40:06,871 --> 00:40:13,040
In order not to ruin our relationship,
do you think I never put in any effort?

481
00:40:16,936 --> 00:40:18,965
What?

482
00:40:19,604 --> 00:40:22,573
If I came to feed a dog?

483
00:40:23,574 --> 00:40:24,324
Okay.

484
00:40:26,854 --> 00:40:29,606
I got it.

485
00:40:30,043 --> 00:40:32,733
I will not come again.

486
00:41:17,843 --> 00:41:19,291
Oh, that!

487
00:41:19,326 --> 00:41:21,404
It should be today, right?

488
00:41:21,439 --> 00:41:22,822
I know.

489
00:41:22,857 --> 00:41:24,858
But the flower was not delivered.

490
00:41:25,497 --> 00:41:27,234
I know it wouldn't be sent here.

491
00:41:28,417 --> 00:41:32,936
That means to say, you knew much early on
who is the one sending them.

492
00:41:35,764 --> 00:41:37,635
Could it be, you two have met?

493
00:41:37,670 --> 00:41:39,574
Did you keep in contact after that?

494
00:41:39,609 --> 00:41:45,863
I am waiting for such an important phone call
that no man can compare to.

495
00:41:46,783 --> 00:41:48,672
What is that?

496
00:41:49,040 --> 00:41:50,697
Gave me a fright.

497
00:41:52,923 --> 00:41:55,190
Oh, we have got the notice too.

498
00:41:55,280 --> 00:41:57,934
For all the efforts that has been put in,
the result is a little small.

499
00:41:57,969 --> 00:42:01,046
Although it is the same holding, but the concert
and album are going to be promoted differently.

500
00:42:01,081 --> 00:42:02,716
Adjust it after the meet up.

501
00:42:02,751 --> 00:42:04,668
But the meeting ground becomes a problem.

502
00:42:04,703 --> 00:42:07,803
Can you not squabble with me
over these small matters?

503
00:42:08,721 --> 00:42:11,423
My life's motivation steams from those.

504
00:42:11,458 --> 00:42:13,830
I will go to your company.

505
00:42:27,871 --> 00:42:29,747
<i>The essay selection's announcement
on September 10th.</i>

506
00:42:29,748 --> 00:42:31,748
<i>Results can be viewed on the
cultural daily paper or website.</i>

507
00:42:33,688 --> 00:42:36,448
If the individual was selected,
will they inform the person?

508
00:42:37,306 --> 00:42:39,057
Heard that, one or two days before,
they will be informed.

509
00:42:39,277 --> 00:42:41,715
In order to give a speech,
they have to have a little preparation.

510
00:42:41,964 --> 00:42:42,714
Oh.

511
00:42:46,998 --> 00:42:50,201
Did you happen to hear any news?

512
00:42:52,125 --> 00:42:56,034
